comments.body: Very cool! Maybe `IntegerSequences` is a better name?
Clearly this is more precise, I was afraid of the length of the name. But I am willing to change that. In fact I did it just now: https://github.com/OpenLibMathSeq/IntegerSequences.jl
@nkottary, is the right way to proceed here with a renamed package to close this PR and trigger a new registration process?
Either that or calling register() again should be fine too. The only thing we don't update is the title of this PR. Everything else should be fine.
